item.title: WandaVision lands a surprise Grammy nomination
item.description: Fans may have been upset that Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Bettany, and most egregiously Kathryn Hahn, were all overlooked at the recent Primetime Emmy Awards, but it’s not as if WandaVision went home completely empty-handed. Recommended Videos Yes, the Marvel Cinematic Universe’s first Disney Plus series didn’t win any of the eight trophies it was nominated for at the main ceremony, but it did put in a strong showing at the Creative Arts Emmys which were held beforehand, where the reality-bending superhero show scooped three of the 15 gongs it was up for.
